Package: mpt2irt
Type: Package
Title: Bringing Multinomial Processing Tree Models To Item Response Theory To Investigate Response Styles
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-03-24
Author: Hansjoerg Plieninger, Daniel W. Heck
Maintainer: Hansjoerg Plieninger <plieninger@uni-mannheim.de>
Imports: checkmate,
    coda,
    doParallel,
    foreach,
    mail,
    MASS,
    MBESS,
    parallel,
    rstan,
    runjags,
    truncnorm
Description: Fitting hierarchical MPT models to obtain IRT estimates for
    different response processes. At the moment, only response style models are
    implemented (separating bias towards middle category, extreme responding, and
    acquiesence). Requires the MCMC samplers JAGS and/or Stan.
License: GPL-2
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    mail,
    reshape2,
    tidyr
